installationInstructions.author: Robert from Sandston, VA
installationInstructions.title: water and ice maker stopped working
installationInstructions.content: Removed the cover on the bottom of the rear of the fridge and the top left of the fridge where the tubbes exit.. Then just simply disconnect the tube coming from the fridge and the supply line. Next go inside the fridge, remove the cover of the filter mount, and remove the 2 screws securing the filter mount in place.  Now pull the tubes through the opening and reinstall in reverse order.
